y direct-to-video films or TV movies, and no red links or redirecting links. -->\n{| class=\"sortable\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#dae3e7; text-align:center;\"\n! Month !! Date !! Name !! Age !! Nationality !! Profession !! Films\n|- align=\"top\"\n|-\n! rowspan=18 style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top;\"| [[Deaths in January 2020|January]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''4'' || [[Tom Long (actor)|Tom Long]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 51 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Australian || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Actor || {{hlist|''[[The Dish]]''|''[[The Book of Revelation (film)|The Book of Revelation]]''}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''8'' || [[Edd Byrnes]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 86 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| American || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Actor || {{hlist|''[[Grease (film)|Grease]]''|''[[The Secret Invasion]]''}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''8'' || [[Buck Henry]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 89 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| American || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Actor, Screenwriter, Director || {{hlist|''[[The Graduate (film)|The Graduate]]''|''[[Heaven Can Wait (1978 film)|Heaven Can Wait]]''}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''9'' || [[Ivan Passer]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 86 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Czech || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Director, Screenwriter || {{hlist|''[[Born to Win]]''|''[[Cutter's Way]]''}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''10'' || [[Neda Arneri\u0107]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 66 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Serbian || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Actress || {{hlist|''[[Shaft in Africa]]''|''[[The Sensual Man]]''}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''12'' || [[Tony Garnett]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 83 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| English || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Producer || {{hlist|''[[Kes (film)|Kes]]''|''[[Earth Girls Are Ea