 Super Globe\n| next = 2007 IHF Super Globe\n}}\n\nThe '''2002 [[IHF Super Globe]]''' was the second edition. It was held in [[Doha]], [[Qatar]] from 3\u20139 June 2002.\nThere were just one group playing against each other, so the group ranking was the final ranking.\n\n[[Al Sadd Handball Team|Al Sadd]] won the title for the first time.\n\n==Round Robin==\n{{Handball table start}}\n{{hbt-row |team={{flagicon|QAT}} [[Al Sadd Handball Team|Al Sadd]] |bg=a |w=4 |d=0 |l=0 |gf=140 |ga=96}}\n{{hbt-row |team={{flagicon|GER}} [[SC Magdeburg]] |bg= |w=3 |d=0 |l=1 |gf=143 |ga=121}}\n{{hbt-row |team={{flagicon|BRA}} [[Metodista S\u00e3o Bernardo]] |bg= |w=2 |d=0 |l=2 |gf=110 |ga=116}}\n{{hbt-row |team={{flagicon|CMR}} [[FAP Yaound\u00e9]] |bg= |w=0 |d=1 |l=3 |gf=105 |ga=132}}\n{{hbt-row |team={{flagicon|KUW}} [[Al-Salmiya SC]] |bg= |w=0 |d=1 |l=3 |gf=108 |ga=141}}\n{{Handball table end}}\n==Match Results==\n{{handballbox\n|date= \n|time= \n|team1= Al Sadd SC {{flagicon|QAT}}\n|score= 39 \u2013 22\n|team2= {{flagicon|CMR}} FAP Yaound\u00e9\n|report=\n|goals1= \n|goals2= \n|HT= 21 \u2013 8\n|twomin1= \n|yellow1=\n|red1= \n|twomin2=\n|yellow2=\n|red2= \n|stadium=\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|refnat=\n}}\n----\n{{handballbox\n|date= \n|time= \n|team1= Metodista S\u00e3o Bernardo {{flagicon|BRA}}\n|score= 35 \u2013 26\n|team2= {{flagicon|KUW}} Al-Salmiya SC\n|report=\n|goals1= \n|goals2= \n|HT= 19 \u2013 13\n|twomin1= \n|yellow1=\n|red1= \n|twomin2=\n|yellow2=\n|red2= \n|stadium=\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|refnat=\n}}\n----\n{{handballbox\n|date= \n|time= \n|team1= Al-Salmiya SC {{flagicon|KUW}}\n|score= 31 \u2013 31\n|team2= {{flagicon|CMR}} FAP Yaound\u00e9\n|report=\n|goals1= \n|goals2= \n|HT= 16 \u2013 13\n|twomin1= \n|yellow1=\n|red1= \n|twomin2=\n|yellow2=\n|red2= \n|stadium=\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|refnat=\n}}\n----\n{{handballbox\n|date= \n|time= \n|team1= SC Magdeburg {{flagicon|GER}}\n|score= 32 \u2013 35\n|team2= {{flagicon|QAT}} Al Sadd SC\n|report=\n|goals1= \n|goals