ago Building|World's Congress Auxiliary Building]]\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon image|Flag of the Cape Colony 1876-1910.svg}} [[Kimberley, Northern Cape|Kimberley]], [[Cape Colony]] \u2013 [[South African and International Exhibition]]<ref name=\"whatremains\">{{cite web|url=http://whatremains.info/1892-kimberley/|title=1892 Kimberley South African and International Exposition \u2013 What Remains|accessdate=29 September 2019}}</ref>\n* 1893 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1891}} [[New York City]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[World's Fair Prize Winners' Exposition (1893)]]\n* 1894 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1891}} [[San Francisco]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[California Midwinter International Exposition of 1894]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1894 \u2013 {{flagicon|Belgium}} [[Antwerp (city)|Antwerp]], [[Belgium]] \u2013 [[Exposition Internationale d'Anvers (1894)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1894 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Lyon]]s, [[French Third Republic|France]] \u2013 [[Exposition internationale et coloniale (1894)|Exposition internationale et coloniale]]<ref name=p425 />\n* 1894 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Manchester]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[British and Colonial Exhibition]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1894 \u2013 {{flagicon|Portugal|1830}} [[Oporto]], [[Portugal]] \u2013 [[Exposi\u00e7\u00e3o Insular e Colonial Portugueza (1894)]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1895 \u2013 {{flagicon|Tasmania}} [[Hobart]], [[Tasmania]] \u2013 [[Tasmanian International Exhibition (1895)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1895 \u2013 {{flagicon|Victoria}} [[Ballarat, Victoria|Ballarat]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]] \u2013 [[Australian Industrial Exhibition (1895)]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1895 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Bordeaux]], [[France]] \u2013 {{ill|Bordeaux Exposition|fr|Exposition_de_Bordeaux_(1895)}}\n* 1895 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1891}} [[Atlanta, Georgia|A