r}} [[Stuttgart]], [[Weimar Republic|Germany]] \u2013 Werkbund Exhibition\n* 1928 \u2013 {{flagicon|Germany|Weimar}} [[Cologne]], Germany \u2013 [[Pressa|International Press Exhibition]]\n* 1928 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1912}} [[Long Beach, California|Long Beach]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[Pacific Southwest Exposition (1928)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1929 \u2013 {{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Newcastle upon Tyne]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[North East Coast Exhibition]]\n* 1929 \u2013 {{flagicon|China|1912}} [[Hangzhou]], [[Republic of China (1912\u20131949)|Republic of China]] \u2013 [[1929 Westlake exposition|Westlake Exposition]]\n* 1929\u20131930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Spain|1874}} [[Seville]], [[Spain]] \u2013 [[Ibero-American Exposition]]\n* 1929\u20131930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Spain|1874}} [[Barcelona, Spain]],<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" /> \u2013 [[1929 Barcelona International Exposition]]\n\n==1930s==\n* 1930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Belgium}} [[Antwerp (city)|Antwerp]], [[Belgium]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" /> \u2013 Exposition internationale coloniale, maritime et d'art flamand\n* 1930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Belgium}} [[Li\u00e8ge (city)|Li\u00e8ge]], [[Belgium]]<ref name=\"FindPelp416\">{{cite encyclopedia\n | title = Appendix B:Fair Statistics\n | encyclopedia = Encyclopedia of World's Fairs and Expositions\n | page=416\n | editor-last = Pelle\n | editor-first = Findling\n | publisher = McFarland & Company, Inc\n | year = 2008\n | id =\n | isbn = 978-0-7864-3416-9\n | accessdate = }}</ref> \u2013 [[Exposition of 1930 (Li\u00e8ge)|Exposition internationale de la grande industrie, sciences et applications, art wallon ancien]]\n* 1930 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Oran, Algeria]] \u2013 [[Oran Exposition]]\n* 1930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Germany|1930}} [[Dresden]], [[Germany]] \u2013 [[International Hygiene Exposition]]\n* 1930 \u2013 {{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]] \u2013 [[Stockholm International 