iale%20genoa%201854&f=false|title=Rivista di Firenze e bullettino delle arti del disegno ...|last=|first=|date=1858|publisher=|isbn=|location=|pages=208|language=it}}</ref>\n* 1854 \u2013 {{flagicon|Kingdom of Bavaria}} [[Munich]], [[Kingdom of Bavaria|Bavaria]] \u2013 Allgemeine deutsche Industrie-Ausstellung<ref name=\"oldbutsecondarybook\">{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/fournationalexhi00lowe|page=[https://archive.org/details/fournationalexhi00lowe/page/28 28]|accessdate=22 April 2012|title=Four national exhibitions in London and their organiser. With portraits and illustrations (1892)|publisher=London, T. F. Unwin|last=Lowe|first=Charles|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170604085029/https://archive.org/details/fournationalexhi00lowe|archive-date=4 June 2017|url-status=live|year=1892}}</ref>\n* 1854 \u2013 {{flagicon|Victoria}} [[Melbourne]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]] \u2013 Melbourne Exhibition (in conjunction with [[Exposition Universelle (1855)]])<ref name=\"oldbutsecondarybook\" />\n* 1855 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Paris]], [[Second French Empire|France]] \u2013 [[Exposition Universelle (1855)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" /><ref name=\"oldbutsecondarybook\" />\n*1856 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Belgium}} [[Brussels]], [[Belgium]] \u2013 International Exhibition<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=F8rUAAAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA57&lpg=RA1-PA57&dq=international+exhibition+of+domestic+economy+1869+amsterdam#v=onepage&q=international%20exhibition%20of%20domestic%20economy%201869%20amsterdam&f=false|title=The Monthly Chronicle of North-country Lore and Legend: V.1-5; Mar. 1887-Dec. 1891|date=1887|publisher=W. Scott}}</ref> \n* 1857 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Manchester]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[Art Treasures Exhibition]] at the [[Stretford|Royal Botanical Gardens, Stretford]]<ref name=\"FindPelp422\" />\n* 1857 \u2013 {{Flagicon|Switzerland}} [[Lausanne]], [[Switzerland]] \