in]], [[German Empire|Germany]] \u2013 International Fisheries Exhibition<ref name=\":2\" />\n*1880 \u2013 {{Flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[Glasgow]], [[United Kingdom]] \u2013 Glasgow Electrical Exhibition<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=weyVDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA143&lpg=PA143&dq=glasgow+electrical+exhibition+1880#v=onepage&q=glasgow%20electrical%20exhibition%201880&f=false|title=Literary Illumination: The Evolution of Artificial Light in Nineteenth-Century Literature|last=Leahy|first=Richard|date=2018-08-15|publisher=University of Wales Press|isbn=9781786832696}}</ref><ref name=\":1\" />\n* 1880\u20131881 \u2013 {{flagicon|Victoria}} [[Melbourne]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]] \u2013 [[Melbourne International Exhibition (1880)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1881 \u2013 {{flagicon|South Australia}} [[Adelaide, South Australia]], [[Australia]] \u2013 [[Adelaide Exhibition]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article47099483|title=THE ADELAIDE EXHIBITION.|date=1881-07-21|work=South Australian Register (Adelaide, SA : 1839 \u2013 1900)|access-date=2019-10-30|pages=4}}</ref>\n* 1881\u20131882 \u2013 {{flagicon|Western Australia}} [[Perth, Western Australia]], [[Australia]] \u2013 [[Perth International Exhibition]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://trove.nla.gov.au/newspaper/article/65960064|title=Inauguration Day|last=|first=|date=16 November 1881|work=Exhibition supplement to The Inquirer|access-date=16 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 1881 - {{flagicon|Cuba|1881}} [[Matanzas, Cuba]] - [[Exhibition of Matanzas]]\n* 1881 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1877}} [[Milwaukee, Wisconsin]] \u2013 [[Milwaukee Industrial Exposition]]{{citation needed|date=December 2018}}\n* 1881 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Paris]], [[France]] \u2013 [[International Exposition of Electricity, Paris]]<ref name=\"FindPelp424\" />\n* 1881 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1877}} [[Atlanta, Georgia|Atlanta]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[International Cotton Exposition]