a e Ultramar|last2=Correia|first2=Jos\u00e9 Candido|date=1888|publisher=Lisboa : Imprensa nacional|others=Robarts \u2013 University of Toronto}}</ref>\n* 1888 \u2013 {{flagicon|Denmark}} [[Copenhagen]], [[Denmark]] \u2013 [[The Nordic Exhibition of 1888]] (Nordiske Industri-Landbrugs og Kunstudstilling)<ref name=\"p425\" />\n* 1889 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Paris]], [[French Third Republic|France]] \u2013 [[Exposition Universelle (1889)]] \u2013 [[Eiffel Tower]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1889 \u2013 {{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Dunedin]], [[New Zealand]] \u2013 [[New Zealand and South Seas Exhibition (1889)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1889 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1877}} [[Buffalo, New York|Buffalo]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[International Industrial Fair (1889)]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n\n==1890s==\n* 1890 \u2013 {{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Vienna]], [[Austria-Hungary]] \u2013 [[Agricultural and Forestry Exposition]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1890 \u2013 {{flagicon|Germany|empire}} [[Bremen (city)|Bremen]], [[German Empire|Germany]] \u2013 Nord-West-Deutsche Gewerbe und Industrie-Ausstellung<ref name=\"p425\" />\n* 1890 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[London]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[International Exhibition of Mining and Metallurgy]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1890 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Edinburgh]], [[United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[International Exhibition of Science, Art & Industry]]<ref name=Edinburgh />\n* 1891 \u2013 {{flagicon|Russian Empire}} [[Moscow]], [[Russian Empire|Russia]] \u2013 Exposition fran\u00e7aise{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1891 \u2013 {{flagicon|Germany|empire}} [[Frankfurt, Germany|Frankfurt]], [[German Empire|Germany]] \u2013 [[International Electro-Technical Exhibition \u2013 1891]]{{citation needed|date=March 2019}}\n* 1891 \u2013 {{flagicon image|Flag of Jamaica (1875\u20131906).svg}} [[Kingston, Jamaica|Kingston]], [[Jamaica]] \u2013 International Exhibition (1891)<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1891 \u2013 {{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Prague]], [[Austria-Hungary]] \u2013 [[General Land Centennial Exhibition (1891)]] at the Prague Exhibition Grounds [https://web.archive.org/web/20051125085402/http://guide.travel.cz/597]\n* 1891 - {{flagicon|Trinidad and Tobago|1891}} [[Port-of-Spain, Trinidad]] - [[Trinidad and Tobago Exhibition]]\n* 1891\u20131892 \u2013 {{flagicon|Tasmania}} [[Launceston, Tasmania|Launceston]], [[Tasmania]] \u2013 Tasmanian International Exhibition (1891)<ref name=p425 />\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Grenoble]], [[France]] \u2013 [[International Alpine Exposition of Grenoble]]\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon|Italy|1861}} [[Genoa]], [[Kingdom of Italy|Italy]] \u2013 Esposizione Italo-Americana (1892)\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1891}} [[Washington, DC]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[Exposition of the Three Americas (1892)]] (never held)<ref name=\"notheldcollection\" />\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[London]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[Crystal Palace Electrical Exhibition]]\n* 1892\u20131893 \u2013 {{flagicon|Spain|1874}} [[Madrid]], [[Spain]] \u2013 [[Historical American Exposition]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" />\n* 1893 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1891}} [[Chicago]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[World's Columbian Exposition]]<ref name=\"FindPelp414\" /> \u2013 [[Palace of Fine Arts, Chicago|Palace of Fine Arts]] and the [[Art Institute of Chicago Building|World's Congress Auxiliary Building]]\n* 1892 \u2013 {{flagicon image|Flag of the Cape Colony 1876-1910.svg}} [[Kimberley, Northern Cape|Kimberley]], [[Cape Colony]] \u2013 [[South African and International Exhibition]]<ref name=\"whatremains\">{{cite web|url=http://whatremains.info/1892-kimberley/|title=1892 Kimberley South African and International Exposition \u2013 What Remains|accessdate=29 September 2019}}</ref>\n* 1893 \u2013 {