ain1899\">{{cite web|url = http://www.studygroup.org.uk/Exhibitions/Pages/Earls%20Court.htm|title = Earls Court|website = Exhibition Study Group|date = 2004|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150711042530/http://www.studygroup.org.uk/Exhibitions/Pages/Earls%20Court.htm|archive-date = 2015-07-11|url-status = dead|access-date = 2014-06-12}}</ref>\n\n==1900s==\n* 1900 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Paris]], [[French Third Republic|France]] \u2013 [[Exposition Universelle (1900)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" /> \u2013 Le Grand Palais\n* 1900 \u2013 {{flagicon|South Australia}} [[Adelaide]], [[South Australia]] \u2013 [[Century Exhibition of Arts and Industries (1900)]]{{citation needed|date=January 2015}}\n* 1901 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1896}} [[Buffalo, New York|Buffalo]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[Pan-American Exposition]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1901 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Glasgow]], [[United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland|United Kingdom]] \u2013 [[Glasgow International Exhibition (1901)]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1901 \u2013 {{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Vienna]], [[Austria-Hungary]] \u2013 [[Bosnische Weihnachts-Ausstellung (1901)]]\n* 1901 \u2013 {{flagicon|United States|1896}} [[Charleston, South Carolina|Charleston]], [[United States]] \u2013 [[South Carolina Inter-State and West Indian Exposition]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1902 \u2013 {{flagicon|Austria-Hungary}} [[Vienna]], [[Austria-Hungary]] \u2013 [[International Fishery Exposition]]\n* 1902 \u2013 {{flagicon|Italy|1861}} [[Turin]], [[Kingdom of Italy|Italy]] \u2013 [[Esposizione Internazionale d'Arte Decorativa Moderna]]<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1902 \u2013 {{flagicon|French Indochina}} [[Hanoi]], [[French Indochina]] \u2013 [[Hanoi exhibition]] (Indo China Exposition Fran\u00e7aise et Internationale)<ref name=\"FindPelp415\" />\n* 1902 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Lille]], [[France]] \u2013 [[International Exposition of Lille]]\n* 1902 \u2013 {{f