ustries (1914)]]{{citation needed|date=January 2018}}\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|France|1794}} [[Lyon]], [[France]] \u2013 [[Exposition internationale urbaine de Lyon]]{{citation needed|date=December 2018}}\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|Japan|1870}} [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]] \u2013 [[Tokyo Taisho Exposition]]\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|German Empire}} [[Cologne]], [[German Empire|Germany]] \u2013 [[Werkbund Exhibition (1914)]]{{citation needed|date=December 2018}}\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Bristol]], [[United Kingdom]] \u2013 International Exhibition (1914)<ref>{{cite news|title=International exhibition became known as a city |url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/International-exhibition-known-city/story-19493585-detail/story.html |newspaper=[[Bristol Post]] |date=2013-07-09 |accessdate=2014-01-28 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201192130/http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/International-exhibition-known-city/story-19493585-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-02-01 }}</ref>\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|UKGBI}} [[Nottingham]], [[United Kingdom]] \u2013 Universal Exhibition (1914) (work begun on site 1913 but never held)<ref name=\"pandpnott\">{{cite news|url=http://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/cgi-bin/paperspast?a=d&d=HNS19131209.2.3|newspaper=Hawera & Normanby Star|location=New Zealand|date=9 December 1913|title=Hawera Chamber of Commerce|page=2|volume=65|accessdate=2014-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324142807/http://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/cgi-bin/paperspast?a=d&d=HNS19131209.2.3|archive-date=24 March 2014|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Anniversaries|url=http://www.thorotonsociety.org.uk/news/thornews_winter201213.htm|first=Ken|last=Brand|date=2012-12-22|accessdate=2014-01-28|publisher=[[Thoroton Society of Nottinghamshire]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202131332/http://www.thorotonsociety.org.uk/news/thornews_winter201213.htm|archive-date=2014-02-02|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 1914 \u2013 {{flagicon|N